  "description": {
    "S": "This easy Asian-inspired Mongolian Noodles recipe brings bold flavors to your table in just 30 minutes. Tender ramen noodles are tossed with perfectly browned ground beef and crisp vegetables in a savory-sweet sauce made with soy sauce, hoisin, and fresh ginger. It's a satisfying, restaurant-quality meal that's perfect for busy weeknights."
